I can’t believe you’re 2 today my sweet baby… 2 years ago today I was terrified but never been happier and more at peace. God knew I needed you. You are the smartest, sweetest, life of the party, wittiest boy in the world. I pray you continue to flourish, embrace all the finer things and also simple pleasures in life. I pray that you stay protected and never lose that confidence and heart of yours. Today I shower you with gifts but the reality is, you gifted me with the best gift in the world being your mommy. A title that I am the most proud of and hold dearest to me. You are my strength. You are my pride. You are my heart. The world is yours my baby. I love you forever. Happy 2nd Birthday my love 🥹💙🥂🥳😘 [Thank you babe @balloondistrict_ @yepchristina]
